column3: OK, tested this with fail commits on either side of MAX_BLOCK_SIZE, so this is ready for ACKs when it finishes the next test run.\n

Just out of interest, can you link to the git diff as well? I've tried 

https://code.google.com/r/bluemattme-bitcoinj/source/browse/core/src/test/java/com/google/bitcoin/core/BitcoindComparisonTool.java?name=blocktester

as you mention in the README that accompanies the jars, but it seems broken.
ACK, I suppose. Any chance of getting this stuff cleaned up and upstreamed?\n
Meh, the upstream bitcoinj stuff is broken and I'm lazy...maybe at some point I'll do that, but for now I dont care so much.\n
